PN,30301
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779401472
OL,3,CYouTube and TikTok failing to protect
OL,4,Cchildren - Ofcom
OL,6,FOfcom has said TikTok and YouTube have
OL,7,Ffailed to outline how they will
OL,8,Fprotect children on their services and
OL,9,Fhas vowed to "force through" more
OL,10,Fchanges when it comes to online safety.
OL,12,FThe communications watchdog said the
OL,13,Ftwo social media platforms had failed
OL,14,Fto set out how they would make the
OL,15,Fcontent feeds, which are pushed to
OL,16,Fchildren, on their services safe,
OL,17,Fdespite being asked to explain how
OL,18,Fthey would do so by the end of April.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779401472
OL,3,CYouTube and TikTok failing to protect
OL,4,Cchildren - Ofcom
OL,6,FThe regulator said neither firm had
OL,7,F"committed to any significant changes
OL,8,Fin response to our specific demands",
OL,9,Fmaintaining that their feeds are
OL,10,F"already safe for children".
OL,12,FOfcom said its own research, published
OL,13,Fon Thursday, showed that "personalised
OL,14,Ffeeds are the primary route through
OL,15,Fwhich children encounter harmful
OL,16,Fcontent" online.
OL,18,FIts children's online safety tracker
OL,19,Fcompared young people's experiences
OL,20,Fbefore and after online safety duties
OL,21,Fcame into effect in July 2025.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@dO]rD@AOUrD@[O]uD@ZOUxD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779401472
OL,3,CYouTube and TikTok failing to protect
OL,4,Cchildren - Ofcom
OL,6,FFindings showed about seven in 10
OL,7,Fchildren aged 11-17 surveyed in
OL,8,FNovember and December last year said
OL,9,Fthey had experienced harmful content
OL,10,Fonline, which was a similar level
OL,11,Freported in the research carried out
OL,12,Fin March and April of that year.
OL,14,FPersonal feeds remained the most
OL,15,Flikely route through which 11-17 year-
OL,16,Folds said they were exposed to harmful
OL,17,Fcontent (35%) ` a similar proportion
OL,18,Fto findings from before the new duties
OL,19,Fcame into effect (37%).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779401472
OL,3,CYouTube and TikTok failing to protect
OL,4,Cchildren - Ofcom
OL,6,FThe research showed that while more
OL,7,Fchildren told an adult about harmful
OL,8,Fcontent they had seen, the proportion
OL,9,Fremained low at 15%, up from 10%
OL,10,Fbefore the duties came into force.
OL,12,FMore than half (51%) of children
OL,13,Fsurveyed said they had been asked to
OL,14,Fprove their age to access content
OL,15,Fonline, up from 41% ` with facial
OL,16,Fscanning the most common method,
OL,17,Ffollowed by uploading a passport or ID
OL,18,For taking a selfie for verification.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779401472
OL,3,CYouTube and TikTok failing to protect
OL,4,Cchildren - Ofcom
OL,6,FHowever, the research also showed nine
OL,7,Fin 10 children aged eight-12 are using
OL,8,Fonline services with a minimum age
OL,9,Frequirement of 13, leading the
OL,10,Fregulator to warn that "firms'
OL,11,Fresponses to our demand to enforce
OL,12,Fthese requirements more effectively
OL,13,Fare concerning".
OL,26,@rD@XOUuD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779401472
OL,3,CYouTube and TikTok failing to protect
OL,4,Cchildren - Ofcom
OL,6,FOfcom said while Snapchat, Facebook,
OL,7,FInstagram and TikTok ` which all have
OL,8,Fa minimum age of 13 in their terms of
OL,9,Fuse ` recognise the importance of
OL,10,Fminimum age policies, the regulator is
OL,11,F"not currently convinced" existing
OL,12,Fcommitments by any of them "ensure
OL,13,Fthey will effectively prevent children
OL,14,Funder 13 from accessing their sites
OL,15,Fand apps".
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@YO]tD@\OUwD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779401472
OL,3,CYouTube and TikTok failing to protect
OL,4,Cchildren - Ofcom
OL,6,FThe watchdog said messaging service
OL,7,FSnapchat, gaming platform Roblox, and
OL,8,FMeta ` which owns Instagram and
OL,9,FFacebook ` had all agreed to adopt
OL,10,Ffurther safety measures to protect
OL,11,Fchildren from online grooming.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779401472
OL,3,CYouTube and TikTok failing to protect
OL,4,Cchildren - Ofcom
OL,6,FIt said adult strangers will be
OL,7,Fprevented from contacting children on
OL,8,FSnapchat by default, children will no
OL,9,Flonger be encouraged to expand their
OL,10,Ffriendship groups to people they do
OL,11,Fnot know and that the platform had
OL,12,Fagreed to "roll out highly effective
OL,13,Fage-checks to all users over the
OL,14,Fsummer to ensure that all under-18s in
OL,15,Fthe UK benefit from these new safety
OL,16,Fmeasures".
OL,26,@tD@KOUxD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779401472
OL,3,CYouTube and TikTok failing to protect
OL,4,Cchildren - Ofcom
OL,6,FRoblox, which has previously faced
OL,7,Fcriticism over its approach to safety,
OL,8,Fhas committed to giving parents the
OL,9,Fability to switch off direct chat
OL,10,Fservices entirely for under-16s, the
OL,11,Fwatchdog said.
OL,13,FMeanwhile, Meta plans to use
OL,14,Fartificial intelligence (AI) tools to
OL,15,Fdetect sexualised conversations
OL,16,Fbetween adults and teens in Instagram
OL,17,Fdirect messages, Ofcom added.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779401472
OL,3,CYouTube and TikTok failing to protect
OL,4,Cchildren - Ofcom
OL,6,FBut the regulator said it was
OL,7,Fscrutinising further details it had
OL,8,Frequested from Meta, TikTok and
OL,9,FYouTube, "given the particularly high
OL,10,Flevels of usage of these services, on
OL,11,Fhow they detect and prevent children
OL,12,Fbeing exposed to harmful content".
OL,14,FThe watchdog pledged to take
OL,15,Fenforcement action, which could
OL,16,Finclude a fine, if it finds services
OL,17,F"are not complying with their duties
OL,18,Fto use appropriate systems to prevent
OL,19,Fchildren's exposure to harmful
OL,20,Fcontent".
OL,26,@qD@JOUtD@aO]yD@AOU|D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779401472
OL,3,CYouTube and TikTok failing to protect
OL,4,Cchildren - Ofcom
OL,6,FDame Melanie Dawes, Ofcom chief
OL,7,Fexecutive, said: "These changes have
OL,8,Fthe potential to make children's lives
OL,9,Fsafer online. Ofcom's sustained public
OL,10,Fand private pressure on the tech
OL,11,Fplatforms where children spend most
OL,12,Ftime has delivered some significant
OL,13,Fsafety improvements ` particularly
OL,14,Fagainst grooming.
OL,26,@oD@ROU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779401472
OL,3,CYouTube and TikTok failing to protect
OL,4,Cchildren - Ofcom
OL,6,F"However, more change is needed, and
OL,7,Fwe remain deeply concerned that,
OL,8,Fdespite overwhelming evidence of harm,
OL,9,Fcompanies are still failing to take
OL,10,Fthe necessary action to keep underage
OL,11,Fchildren off their platforms and make
OL,12,Ftheir feeds safer.
OL,14,F"We are determined to force through
OL,15,Ffurther changes, using the full extent
OL,16,Fof our powers and influence. We will
OL,17,Falso bring our evidence and experience
OL,18,Fto bear as the Government considers
OL,19,Fresponses to its national conversation
OL,20,Fon children's safety and social media."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU|D@gO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/17
