CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779401472
OL,3,CYouTube and TikTok failing to protect
OL,4,Cchildren - Ofcom
OL,6,FAndy Burrows, chief executive of the
OL,7,FMolly Rose Foundation ` set up in the
OL,8,Fmemory of teenager Molly Russell who
OL,9,Ftook her own life after viewing
OL,10,Fharmful content on social media `
OL,11,Fwelcomed Ofcom "starting to bare its
OL,12,Fteeth against Big Tech companies that
OL,13,Fhave been complacent and evasive when
OL,14,Fit comes to protecting children from
OL,15,Fpreventable harm".
OL,26,@sD@POUwD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
