PN,30315
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779401472
OL,3,CYouTube and TikTok failing to protect
OL,4,Cchildren - Ofcom
OL,6,FA Meta spokesperson said they had been
OL,7,F"investing in tools and policies to
OL,8,Fensure teens have safe, positive
OL,9,Fonline experiences" and are "rolling
OL,10,Fout new safety protections for teens",
OL,11,Fadding that the company will "continue
OL,12,Fto engage with Ofcom on these
OL,13,Fimportant issues".
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@SO]qD@]OUrD@eO]sD@^OUuD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/17
