OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30316
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779401472
OL,3,CYouTube and TikTok failing to protect
OL,4,Cchildren - Ofcom
OL,6,FA spokesperson for TikTok said: "It's
OL,7,Fvery disappointing that Ofcom has
OL,8,Ffailed to acknowledge both our
OL,9,Flongstanding and newer safety
OL,10,Ffeatures, from no direct messaging for
OL,11,Funder-16s, pre-set private teen
OL,12,Faccounts, to our recently enhanced age
OL,13,Fassurance technologies. We will
OL,14,Fcontinue to make ongoing investments
OL,15,Fin safety measures for our users."
OL,26,@nD@aOUwD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/17
