PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779401472
OL,3,CYouTube and TikTok failing to protect
OL,4,Cchildren - Ofcom
OL,6,FA YouTube spokesperson said the
OL,7,Fplatform "provides industry-leading,
OL,8,Fage-appropriate, high-quality
OL,9,Fexperiences for young viewers, working
OL,10,Fwith child safety experts to deliver
OL,11,Fprotections that support millions of
OL,12,Ffamilies across the UK", adding that
OL,13,Fits "YouTube Kids, and Kid & Teen
OL,14,FAccounts on YouTube, offer age-
OL,15,Fappropriate experiences with extra
OL,16,Fprotections".
OL,18,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
